A collection of basic algorithms implemented in C created while I took COMP10002 (Foundations of Algorithms). I vibe coded some visualisations to better show them.

Implemented so far:

Sorting Algorithms:
- Quicksort -> make quicksort
- Bubble Sort -> make bubble_sort 
- Insertion Sort -> make insertion_sort
- Heapsort -> make heapsort
- Bogosort
- Mergesort -> make mergesort

Search:
- Linear Search -> make linear_search
- Binary Search -> make binary_search

Pattern Search:
- Naive Pattern Search -> make naive_pattern_search
- Knuth Morris Pratt (KMP) -> make kmp
- Boyer Moore Horspool (BMH) -> make bmh
- Suffix Array Pattern Search -> make suffix_array_pattern_search

Graphs:
- BFS and DFS -> make bfs_and_dfs
